Tile art assets used by CitySim are from Micropolis, Unix Version, which was released for the Unix platform in or about 1990 and was modified for inclusion in the One Laptop Per Child program. 
These assets are licensed under the terms of the GNU General Public License version 3.0, as published by the Free Software Foundation.
See the LICENSE file in the "images/tiles" directory for more information.

